<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">Why Choose Cliff Mortgages for Your FHA Loan</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        Navigating a government-backed loan can feel overwhelming. We work closely with our FHA lender partners to help make the process smoother, clearer, and more manageable for you.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap text-3xl text-[#5c3f14] mb-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">FHA Guidelines Made Understandable</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">FHA loans come with specific rules and requirements. We explain what to expect, identify potential hurdles early, and coordinate with lenders who specialize in FHA programs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-users text-3xl text-[#5c3f14] mb-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">Support for First-Time Buyers</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We regularly work with first-time homebuyers using FHA financing. We answer questions, explain next steps, and help you feel informed and confident throughout the process.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-hands-holding-child text-3xl text-[#5c3f14] mb-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-gray-800">Gift Fund &amp; DPA Guidance</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We help you understand how gift funds work and connect you with lender options or programs that may accommodate Down Payment Assistance (DPA), depending on your scenario.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">The FHA Advantage: Your Path to Homeownership</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
        An FHA loan is designed to make buying a home accessible, especially if you have less-than-perfect credit or a smaller down payment.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-center items-stretch">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-2 border-[#5c3f14]">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-[#09143e]">FHA Loan</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house-flag text-4xl text-[#5c3f14] my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Low 3.5% Down Payment:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">Requirement makes homeownership more attainable.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Flexible Credit Scores:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">Guidelines are more forgiving than conventional loans.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Gift Funds Allowed:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">Your down payment may come entirely from a family gift.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-800">Conventional Loan</h3>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake text-4xl text-gray-500 my-4" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-left text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Higher Down Payment Often Needed:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">3–5% down is possible, but often paired with higher credit score requirements.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Stricter Credit Requirements:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">Typically requires a credit score of 620 or higher.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-times text-red-400 mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-2">
              <div class="col-span-4 font-semibold">Gift Fund Rules Can Be Stricter:</div>
              <div class="col-span-8">Some programs require a portion of the buyer’s own funds.</div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

